{"tid":826172,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"里奧︰要曼聯爭歐聯係要求太高","createTime":"2018-09-18T05:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T08:42:34.000Z","uid":4492,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b25f3233beee7213f4dce97f1c511f5af1fc8478","tid":826172,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"曼聯名將里奧費迪南表示，現階段的紅魔仍在重建當中，要他們在歐聯爭取奪冠是太高的要求。<br />\n<br />\n朗尼曾經為離開愛華頓而煩惱<br />\n<br />\n里奧費迪南說︰「曼聯一直有壓力要在歐聯走得更遠，但這隊曼聯不是10年前那一隊，在本土一直稱霸而歐聯又最少打入4強。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「現在球隊仍在重建當中，他們在聯賽尚未贏得冠軍，很難期望可打入4強。像上屆般被西維爾意外淘汰的情景不是很好，但足球正是這樣。今屆分組賽的賽事十分難打，但亦很刺激。我想祖雲達斯有C朗在陣可望出線，而摩連奴在歐聯亦有他的辦法。」<br />\n<br />\n「雖然我不想說，但曼城及利物浦的確是有力爭歐聯的球隊，是唯獨2支可以爭冠的英格蘭球隊。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e6ca4d2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\nRIO呢條25仔手指拗出唔拗入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcd374cba8acb6144e7decdcb926af3cd538a8b","tid":826172,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢算啦"},{"pid":"3813d12ec6f1164f4d8d6753d9e1ac4241cae112","tid":826172,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"廢老說三道四又拎自己十年前打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfeef3c97d3cba276db010fe177529ebc30f889","tid":826172,"uid":42246,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"明明我車榜首 提都唔提下<br />\n屌你老母係咪咁唔比面呀<br />\n抵泰利笑鳩你細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eebdd3d7b5116656bbcd3a796ce7c6aef08ed15","tid":826172,"uid":69115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊歐